; Coverage test for xact.cc line 595
; Tests null posting balance when the balance is a long integer type.
; When all postings use commodityless amounts (bare numbers), the balance
; may be stored as a long/integer internally. The null posting path must
; handle is_long() by converting to amount via to_amount().

2024/01/01 Test long balance
    Expenses:A                       5
    Assets:B

test bal
                  -5  Assets:B
                   5  Expenses:A
--------------------
                   0
end test
